"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"据官方消息，Ergo生态网站Sigmaverse新增了一项应用——Ergo Payment Portal（Ergo支付门户）。商家和个人可使用此支付门户就其产品和服务接受ERG付款。该dApp旨在方便小商家和个人使用Ergo支付。它提供了一种在其他应用中整合Ergo或SigUSD支付的方法，允许从URL请求支付。\",\"timestamp\":1638897315,\"title\":\"Ergo支付门户上线\"},\"digest\":\"Uod_TRFcOq2RfnMTwCAQSaKq4jQw-zQv358FIhhleBw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xedC503fb8E5512519C1af1f2Fcb4C7B99D7bf635\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ObOZha6MxuW_rqxCYbzyOwQSy_rrZMSQfC54PbNUb20\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q8MwBxrcmQtQRZH7QSmPM2_e9Kt6AZhC02hLbBbacTg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"7r7dSLSK-ssKSaNLj3xc1ctqMc1tpaJAImAoXrVF-4rfj91dk8NOot_cIX9li-en2uYuQppuPZUturmnbzb-gA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa107a6acfb408fe01a17aed74bf6af40e859a5fdb8a77d6c8b5b92d77e6cf8af5e3c7fb4fd0bb556eb0eb993e53abb832832c79ae20c9cc0fe4266daf9379d8f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ObOZha6MxuW_rqxCYbzyOwQSy_rrZMSQfC54PbNUb20\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q8MwBxrcmQtQRZH7QSmPM2_e9Kt6AZhC02hLbBbacTg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Uod_TRFcOq2RfnMTwCAQSaKq4jQw-zQv358FIhhleBw\"}"